title: season 10 is gonna be shit. calling it now
body: if the boards have any indication of what to expect in season 10 then it's gonna be a shit show. everyone on boards is either crying about "bots", crying about client being buggy, crying about poro king being ARAM, crying about mods abusing power, crying about certain champions, crying about wanting free dodges or straight up crying about high damage. this will be a rough season.
